lead_paragraph: Missing out on the Premier League title last season will have no bearing on Tottenham Hotspur's state of mind when they meet champions Leicester at White Hart Lane on Saturday, manager Mauricio Pochettino said.

headline.print_headline: Last Season Irrelevant to Leicester Game-Pochettino
